Business Brief -- Viacom International Inc.:
   Firm Revises Credit Pact,
   Extends Revolving Portion
Sumner M. Redstone, chairman, and Frank J. Biondi Jr.,
president and chief executive, said "the enhanced flexibility
of the credit facility will enable us to further pursue
opportunities for our businesses and our financial
restructuring program."
   Viacom International is a unit of Viacom Inc., which in
turn is 75.5%-owned by closely held National Amusements Inc.